* payable

Equity
= Assets - Liabilities


Registration: K=income/registrations D=liability
Payment: D=cash K=liability
Event: +expense -cash | +income +cash
Bank transaction: +cash -bank | -cash +bank
Pay teacher cash: +expense -cash
Teacher performs services: +expense +liability
Pay teacher check: +expense -bank
